node.text: Here's @bengizmo  from @haven_pro  and @kalebsaleeby  talking about "snapshot IAQ monitoring". One of the great things about the HAVEN Central Air Monitor is that it is a permanent installation inside the ductwork, and the HAVEN Pro Portal is a contractor-only platform where data can be viewed remotely, and reports for homeowners can be generated!
